articles.title: About this site
articles.description:
This site is in its infancy!
   I have built this initial site to display my coding experience in R and RStudio, as I continue to expand the site, you can check back in as I fill the website with professional and explorative components
articles.contents:
Deliverables from my Master’s thesis (Decision-making guide and Institutional Analysis)

Exploratory video editing
